{
  "text": "Nowadays, many different theoretical and practical methods have been proposed for target detection, edge detection is one of the most widely used methods. There are many ways of achieving this goal actually [CITATION_1] , such as Hough transform, Prewitt edge detector, Roberts edge operator, Canny edge detector, Sobel edge detector, Marr-Hildreth and Marr-Poggio operators.",
  "citation_candidates": [
